bootstrap.summary: Expedited initial setup for any developer by installing and configuring dependencies and other key development environment setup activities.

deploy.summary: Deploy smart contracts from AlgoKit compliant repository.

generate.summary: Generate code for an Algorand project (e.g., typed ApplicationClient from ARC-32 application.json).

init.summary: Initializes a new project from a template, including prompting for template specific questions to be used in template rendering.

localnet.summary: Manage the AlgoKit LocalNet (start, stop, reset, status, logs, explore, console).
